Strongcoin,is,a,hybrid,wallet,Bitcoin,service,The,wallet,is,browser,encrypted,to,prevent,anyone,from,having,access,to,the,Bitcoin,address,except,the,owner,The,service,does,not,require,a,specified,Bitcoin,address,format,so,users,can,move,coins,to,and,from,to,other,services,without,needing,to,alter,an,address,StrongCoin,merchant,API,allows,users,to,accept,Bitcoins,as,payments,on,merchant,websites,The,API,functions,allow,users,to,create,orders,and,handle,payment,notifications